{"tid":1672469,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對香港未來我有一個大膽既想法","createTime":"2019-10-24T06:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T15:51:37.000Z","uid":53604,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dbd3428fe761f5179fb0aab4db82d6eea62575ff","tid":1672469,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:28:31.000Z","msg":"<ins>首先我唔熟經濟, 我係想知行唔行得通先貼上黎問</ins><br />\n我係度諗點解加密貨幣既然理論上咁好點解一直不能成為主流<br />\n我估主要係信心問題<br />\n錢之所以係錢而唔係大富翁玩具錢，係因為大眾都認為錢係代表某種價值<br />\n而加密貨幣就說服唔到大眾佢係有價值，而最後大家都會將加密貨幣換返做美金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果....<br />\n如果香港完全放棄港元，轉用加密貨幣做交易，會唔會說服到其他國家跟？<br />\n好似瑞士咁係國際洗黑錢中心，如果有國家跟，到時開創先河既香港就係加密貨幣中心<br />\n會唔會令有心推動加密貨幣成為未來貨幣既勢力支持香港獨立？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得有可能既可以討論下<br />\n覺得 FF 既睇完笑下我on9就算<br />\n<br />\n利申：<strong>我唔係要 promote加密貨幣<br />\n所以唔該唔好貼教人炒加密貨幣d 野乘機呃錢</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40caa5384f4f4d7c5a030ccf8aa2673e0abd958d","tid":1672469,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3534d3308d7c26d5bfbe9d018fba14c0adb3db3","tid":1672469,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:43:50.000Z","msg":"邊有國家想用一個唔受自己操控嘅貨幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f8eab00d43ca9c6f61632b468e7924575fac43","tid":1672469,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd4d7646370a7fca2f1a117e6039e6bbafae6bc","tid":1672469,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3534d3308d7c26d5bfbe9d018fba14c0adb3db3","tid":1672469,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci